Kate Berlant and Jacqueline Novak kick off the wellness conversation! Topics include food habits, yoga mats, matcha, eggs, dairy, dry brushing, Arctic Zero, Gaiam, Lululemon, Tiffany's, the pleasure of consumption, and the comfort of product reviews.
